"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?28/22/29034/contributors\">",
"     Paul Rutgeerts, MD, PhD, FRCP",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
